"{\"uid\": \"www.christianpost.com.-news-eu-denying-europes-christian-roots-contributed-to-brexit-165713--Part2\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"\\\"A United Europe was my great-grandfather's dream,\\\" he said, as we had a friendly debate.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 89, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jonathan, like his famous ancestor, has a broad vision.\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He is concerned for Britain's security in a world where Obama foreign policy has shredded overseas confidence in a friendship with the United States.\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My great-grandfather would have voted 'Remain,'\\\" thinks Jonathan.\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am not sure.\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Churchill's vision was in the context of 1945 Europe.\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a continent struggling to rebuild after the Second World War.\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Europe in 1945 still remembered the First World War, when the august ruling monarchs, most blood-related, went at each other through the sacrifice of their young men.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Churchill wanted a Europe that would live as a community, not an asteroid belt of colliding states.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Further, as Jonathan and I show in detail in God and Churchill, Sir Winston saw the Second World War as being for the survival of \\\"Christian Civilization,\\\" a term he used repeatedly.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One doubts he would be excited about the rabid secularism of the current EU and its abandonment of \\\"Christian Civilization.\\\"\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jonathan and I,